Notable guest stars: Mike Massimino as himself', date: '2012-02-02'},
	{ name: 'Livin\' on a Prayer', number: '12', season_id: '12', description: 'When Stewie\'s new best friend falls ill, Lois takes him to the hospital where she finds out he has a critical, but treatable, disease. However, the boy\'s parents refuse treatment due to their religious beliefs, leaving Lois no choice but to take drastic measures to seek treatment for the boy herself. Meanwhile, Peter has a religious experience of his own.', date: '2012-01-29'},
	{ name: 'Tom Tucker: The Man and His Dream', number: '13', season_id: '12', description: 'When Peter decides to become a famous actor, he becomes Tom Tucker\'s agent as his first step toward stardom. Meanwhile, Chris dates a girl who looks disturbingly like a member of the Griffin household.', date: '2012-02-12'},
	{ name: 'The Super Speedy Cider Squeezy 6000', number: '15', season_id: '13', description: 'Cider Season has come once again and the Apple family is ready to make their famous cider. But this year, two twin colts known as the Flim Flam Brothers arrive to show off their new invention, the super speedy cider squeezy 6000 promising to make more cider in half the time. When they refuse to share business with the twins, the Apple family is instead challenged to a contest. Can Applejack, Granny Smith, Apple Bloom and Big Macintosh pull through and defeat the machine, especially with Sweet Apple Acres on the line? ', date: '2012-01-28'},
